  <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Abacus FHIR Dataset Analytics";
  dcterms:title "Abacus FHIR Dataset";
  dcterms:description "FHIR-based health dataset from the Abacus study, combining structured clinical observations and questionnaire responses. Includes cognitive assessments (Stroop, Digit Span, PVT, Spatial Memory, Word Recall, PaSMO), fall reports, daily routines, body metrics, GPS activity data, and Life-Space Mobility (LSM) questionnaires.";
